content: My cousin (16 years old) wants to work at a call center and I'm not sure if it's allowed or not

Yes your cousin is allowed to phone bank.  We phone bank virtually through zoom and a browser based website.  Here is a link to sign up https://events.democrats.org/event/664004/?utm_source=Discord&utm_medium=Posts&utm_campaign=Daily%20Engagement

Or if they prefer the comfort of Discord our <#1242256751445934262> Mods are here 9am-midnight to connect them with our Dialing Dawn 'til Dusk dialer.  We'd be happy to help! https://events.democrats.org/event/704955/
